PROMS Installation Instructions
-------------------------------

* Copy the installation to the destination machine and change directory to this directory.

* Change the permissions for the installation script to allow execution, e.g:

sudo chmod -R +x ./

* Run the installation script.

sudo ./install.bash

* Change to the PROMS directory:

cd /opt/proms

* Modify the necessary settings in the file settings.py. by changing the base server URIs to match your server name
  or URI. E.g:

# Replace "proms.csiro.com" with your server name or IP address
PROMS_INSTANCE_NAMESPACE_URI = 'http://proms.csiro.com/'
FUSEKI_QUERY_URI = 'http://proms.csiro.com/fuseki/data/query'
FUSEKI_UPDATE_URI = 'http:/proms.csiro.com/fuseki/data/update'
FUSEKI_SECURE_QUERY_URI = 'http://proms.csiro.com/fuseki/data/query'
FUSEKI_SECURE_UPDATE_URI = 'http://proms.csiro.com/fuseki/data/update'

* Run PROMS (while still in the /opt/proms directory):

sudo ./start.bash

* Report any problems to nick.car@csiro.au
